#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/dateToParts.txt:20
msgid ""
"Returns a document that contains the constituent parts of a given BSON "
"Date value as individual properties. The properties returned are "
"``year``, ``month``, ``day``, ``hour``, ``minute``, ``second`` and "
"``millisecond``."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/dateToParts.txt:25
msgid ""
"You can set the ``iso8601`` property to ``true`` to return the parts "
"representing an `ISO week date "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_week_date>`_ instead. This will return"
" a document where the properties are ``isoWeekYear``, ``isoWeek``, "
"``isoDayOfWeek``, ``hour``, ``minute``, ``second`` and ``millisecond``."
msgstr ""

